Class User

java.lang.Object
ducknetwork.domain.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Duck, Person
public abstract class User extends Object
Abstract representation of a user in the social network. Contains common fields and friendship management.

      public void addFriend(User u)
      Add a friend to the local friend list. Repository is responsible for ensuring bidirectional updates; this method only protects against nulls and duplicates.
      Parameters:
      u - friend to add; if null the method is a no-op
